item.title: Game Decision Flow Chart
item.dc:creator: sersoft
item.description:
NakedRobber:

Hey, I just thought gamers might appreciate it so I threw it up for fun. I see our jokes about miserable, lonely virgins hit a little too close to home for you.

Here’s a tip for all you kids out there. If you want to secure your spot at the bottom of the social food chain, make 1600 angry posts on a video game forum and change your avatar to the Windows 3.11 logo. Works every time.

I don’t find flowcharts funny or original, that’s all. If you think it was a personal attack think again, I don’t play any of the games on that pic.

And I would have kept my old avatar forever, but one of the moderators changed it into something fucking retarded, and I couldn’t find my old one anywhere.

Which brings me to the next point, how is your flowchart related to these forums at all? There are no valve games in there.

In my avatar, 3.11 is a reference to valve in their recent Portal 2 ARG, which actually indicated a date, I have almost no interest in windows 3.11.
